- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses a new compositional approach to cognition, which is relevant to AI research. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper discusses the construction of conceptual spaces for various types, which can be used in machine learning applications. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the mathematical underpinnings of the compositional approach to cognition. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also less likely but possible as the paper discusses the construction of conceptual spaces, which can be applied in computer vision tasks.
